##############################################################################

                   bdi-4 branch notes.

 $Author$
 $Date$

##############################################################################

  The sources in this branch were committed as a stop-gap measure in order
  to meet the requirements for compiling with a 2.6 kernel. Now that the
  HEAD of emc2 this branch can now be sidelined.

  All further development should be targeted at HEAD or one of the other
  sanctioned branches. The bdi-4 branch should only receive minor bug fixes.

